{"tid":15664,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣民宿］就出發先黎同我講退訂？","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T10:19:15.000Z","uid":31884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"347d75b4a9de3402b7d333fda50526c89caa78e1","tid":15664,"uid":31884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n差唔多半年前，我一家人準備組團聖誕個期去台灣旅行，有老有嫩，夾夾埋埋都十幾人。<br />\n<br />\n個時我地已經即刻book機票民宿，諗住唔洗挨貴機民宿啦，咁當時都好順利，一屋老幼係到plan緊去邊食野邊到行街既時候，前日民宿個邊就同我講話退返訂比我地。<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢地格黎個間屋早排火燭，驚有陣味，影響到我地，話願意全額退訂。<br />\n<br />\n但我地十幾人有老有嫩，而家先再搵地方都已經好難搵，搵到地方都貴左萬幾兩萬蚊。<br />\n<br />\n我就話唔緊要啦，我地都搵唔到其他地方住，機票又買左，就算真係有陣味都唔介意啦，照住啦。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢又已讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢應該都企硬退訂架啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">我其實係想黎問下各位巴絲打，有無相熟台北民宿/酒店放得落我一家十幾口，唔洗貴成萬幾兩萬蚊，唔想台北訓街呀，我應該點做呀。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10192efe32913b97b3bc89312df3f38dfa21f14","tid":15664,"uid":31884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db714d7111ba35b35da599f132f9eb0a9884f129","tid":15664,"uid":33031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05: